<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/NewRangersJuly18.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1138" title="NewRangersJuly18" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/NewRangersJuly18.jpg" alt="" width="392" height="183" /></a></p>
